{"tid":2387380,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"啲人拎GME事件比喻成黃藍絲，咁有買GME叫咩好？","createTime":"2021-01-30T09:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T09:53:01.000Z","uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9daff1f75ce281c8a8f3b6db8468b15edb709476","tid":2387380,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:30:55.000Z","msg":"啲人話撐大戶機構既係藍絲<br />\n團結一心對抗機構既係黃絲<br />\n咁有買GME叫咩？<br />\n冇買GME又叫咩？<br />\n<br />\n我諗到一個叫流星派，一個叫太陽派"},{"pid":"b9a757cf308f9a6bcf5d8b26f9f9729e0d509410","tid":2387380,"uid":37146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"流星，往往只是一瞬即逝，卻是不知不覺地，綻放永恆的魅力。它們不比太陽耀眼，但卻閃閃發亮，獨特的光芒會讓人驚歎。 我們就是一顆顆的流星， 每一個都同樣有著熾熱的心。當我們集合在一起時，便產生摩擦而燃燒 ，帶來新突破，打破舊有的介限。流星，會燃燒自己的生命，傾盡全力來照亮他人。 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d694cf591875b74ee4b9b2c87beb475556d2345","tid":2387380,"uid":100276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:32:23.000Z","msg":"屌大戶咪一樣可以買上，你估無老散買跌咩"},{"pid":"e55fb28fb73b9b6c7c22ea591ac1500874deed66","tid":2387380,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:49:18.000Z","msg":"但睇真啲原來個粒唔係流星，係隕石，集體衝向地球，造成世界末日，即係股災。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5070a03ae3d39a7c37101c376ebe8554aff3529a","tid":2387380,